  "description": {
    "zh": "这类大家伙的测试不能随便交给谁，我得找个有经验的人。你觉得你够格吗？\n\n你可以选择 ASh-12 突击步枪或者 RSh-12 转轮手枪，装上 30mm 光学瞄具，是的，连转轮也得装，不少 PMC 就是这么干的。带它们去储备站清理点目标，回来告诉我表现如何。\n\n明白了吗？那就行动吧，士兵，别闹出太大动静。",
    "en": "I need these big guns tested by someone experienced, do you think you're good enough for this kind of work?\n\nIt's the ASh-12 assault rifle and the RSh-12 revolver, choose one of them and bring them to the military base. Either of those need to have a 30mm scope attached, yes even the revolver, I saw people like you use them in this configuration before, you operators can be weird at times. Take out some targets there and come back.\n\nUnderstood? Alright then warrior, I'm sure you won't get into too much trouble."
  },
